      "title": "异步编程",
      "language": "javascript",
      "code": "// Promise\nfetch('/api/data')\n    .then(res => res.json())\n    .then(data => console.log(data))\n    .catch(err => console.error(err));\n\n// async/await\nasync function fetchData() {\n    try {\n        const res = await fetch('/api/data');\n        const data = await res.json();\n        return data;\n    } catch (error) {\n        console.error(error);\n    }\n}\n\n// 并行执行\nconst [r1, r2] = await Promise.all([fetch1(), fetch2()]);"
    },
